phrases: Are you looking for something, Ivica?
Is that all you have to say after making me wait for you, Blanc?
The government is still trying to haggle with us.
They are afraid of us foreigners.
We are just a private company.
The sites have always looked like this.
It is the fate of the survivors.
Are you waiting for the girl with turquoise hair to return?
Who else could stop this tragedy?
It is pointless to count the dead in this city.
Why the hell are they flying so low?!
They are going to be in trouble when we get back.
We have our own duties to take care of.
We do not have time to wait.
Still, it is human nature to keep waiting...
Waiting for the dove to return with a branch of hope in its beak.
It felt like the world was going to change!
I do not know if it is for better or worse, but...
Keep your eyes on the road!
Could my body be anymore inconvenient?
Are you are having these dreams because of your spiritual powers?
If you are not even sure that it is going to happen,
why bother taking Noah to a safer spot?
There is going to be a fire!
How can I watch him die?!
He barely settled in the forest.
He has no friends or family.
Ao, you understand that feeling, right?
I have not gathered all the sea mangoes for Mr. Wong yet.
Just do not pass out, or the leeches are going to suck you dry!
If you do not come back on time, I will call the police!
a hundred thousand for delivering the IFO's ECU is easy money.
But Gazelle, are you sure it is a good idea to trust the Japanese army?
And they gave you that weird gadget as well.
Are not they just playing you for a fool?
It is the newest beacon controller.
As long as this is online, the Japanese army will lead us safely and soundly to them.
I am more concerned with what they did not tell us.
If you guys are not interested, feel free to go home.
I will keep all the money.
I am okay, but something is on fire.
The fuck are you doing here, brat?!
You nearly killed me because you cannot drive!
We do not have time to deal with kids!
What the hell are you doing?!
What are we going to do if the cargo gets damaged?
We will not even see a cent of our money!
If there is a transmitter on the case, the Japanese army will wonder why we opened it!
If we were not in a hurry...
I have never seen an ECU act like this.
I cannot do anything about it!
It is your job to do something about it!
I have never seen something like this before.
Hey, where do you think you are going?
You are the kid who lives at Fukai's, right?
You mind lending me an FP?
He must have some spares laying around.
I mean, since he has the money to raise some random foreign kid and all.
Do not just stare at it!
What the hell are you doing?!
You should have learned about this in school!
We cannot do anything about it.
This could turn into an ugly mess!
This may have been an ugly mess all along.
I am already done with today's data...
Sorry, it is time to scramble.
Why cannot you call on another team?
We should let the kids rest.
There was a Scub Coral signal.
That happens all the time, Rebecka!
That is true, but take a look at the location.
The Scub Coral signal that we detected 30 minutes ago
grew rapidly in the past five minutes.
We are still analyzing the data,
but it is telling us that the probability of a Secret emerging is 98.
And this is probably where it will appear.
An area claimed by both the United Okinawan Archipelago and China-Japan.
Will you go if there is a dispatch order?
Get a hold of yourself, Naru!
Tell me I am all right!
We should hurry while we can!
We will not be able to meet up with the Japanese army if we get caught up in this!
I am afraid that light was emitted by a Scub emergence.
But who would be happy with a giant that cannot be used?
We should believe in the people of Okinawa.
We have no choice but to wait.
But a feeling of sadness is plaguing me.
All residents in the Osaki area of Iwato Island must evacuate immediately.
So that thing earlier was really a G-Monster?
I will not be back until tomorrow morning, so go to sleep.
You do not have to take care of me.
It is the responsibility of a parent to send their children to school.
Even if they are not bound by blood.
Gramps, will you take my FP?
How is an old man like me going to drive that thing?
It turned into a real mess, so I was worried.
We believed you will deliver it as agreed.
Unlike Japs, we keep our words.
By the way, there seems to be something missing.
Come on, this is stuff you would eat at a bar.
All that is changing about me is this uniform...
So why does it feel like something is coming to an end?
You are not going to eat your words, right?
If we get back within six hours, the money's ours!
You sound like you are fine.
You should have nursed me yourself if you were so worried.
Your old man would not give me a break if I went over to your place.
I do not know what your mom did,
but it has nothing to do with you.
It is pointless to worry about all that stuff.
Sure, you are a foreigner, but nobody's going to die because of that.
Just think about how much better you are compared to me.
I can never win an argument against her since she is sick.
I hope she will cheer up when I give her this tomorrow.
What are we going to do?
It is not like we have much of a chance.
There is a freaking huge hole in the ground where it is supposed to be.
What if that foreigner kid picked it up?
But then the Scub popped up along with a G-Monster.
Now the Japs deployed their army FPs.
I think we got up caught in something big.
Try listening to the sounds around us.
You cannot hear a single bird or even a bug.
Yuu, be a good girl and look at the camera!
The Scub should not show up twice at the same place!
There is more than one pillar!
This is why I told you to leave the first one alone.
Protecting mankind from emerging unknown creatures
is the job of our company, Generation Blue and our team Pied Piper.
You will dispatch your team of aces for us?
This is quite the exceptional case.
But because of that, I would like to discuss the price as well...
We have yet to sign a contract and he is moving in?
And even if we rushed there now, we would not make it to the Secret in time.
What are you going to do if something happens to the kids in a pointless fight?
At the moment, I am more worried about the children of Iwato Island.
Just get away from the Scub!
A G-Monster could show up any second!
That is the same one from yesterday!
We could not make up, after all.
What the hell's wrong with this thing?
We have been looking for you.
You had it after all, foreigner.
I do not know what this is, but I am not handing it over.
I am not handing it over to anyone!
Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Within the light he discovered through fate,
he found the feelings his mother left for him.
When Ao finds himself in the midst of a battle,
What does he see in this vibrating storm of destruction?
Eureka Seven AO episode 2: Call It What You Want.
Listen to the voice of the children of the stars.
